Title: [Seattle] Spartan Host KVM - Raid 10 SSD, Gigabit, 20Gb/s DDoS Protection

&lt;p&gt;Spartan Host is a dedicated server, VPS and colocation provider with the majority of its hosting operations based in Seattle, Washington. We began hosting Minecraft Servers but have grown exponentially since building up a reputation of being reliable and dedicated to making the customer's experience the best it can be. The following offer is based in Digital Fortress' Downtown Seattle facility that is well known for hosting mission-critical equipment.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Advantages:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Top class facility&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Virtualizor Control Panel&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;RAID 10 Samsung 850 Pro SSD Storage&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;20Gb/s TCP DDoS Protection with a burst of 40Gb/s by CNServers&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;KVM Virtualisation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;IPv6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Network Test Information:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Test IP: 162.252.10.200&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Test File: http://162.252.10.200/100mb.test&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
