&lt;p&gt;1500GB Bandwidth @ 100Mbps inbound/1Gbps outbound&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;20Gb/s TCP DDoS Protection&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1 IPv4 address&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;16 IPv6 addresses&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://billing.spartanhost.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=74"&gt;$4.80 per month with KVM20 coupon code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Both &lt;b&gt;Windows&lt;/b&gt; and &lt;b&gt;Linux&lt;/b&gt; can be installed on our KVM plans. All OS options can be seen at checkout, any special requests can be sent in via &lt;a href="https://billing.spartanhost.net/submitticket.php?step=2&amp;deptid=3"&gt;ticket&lt;/a&gt;. Additional IPv4 addresses are $2 per month.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Not allowed:&lt;/b&gt; Spamming, Camfrog and anything illegal in the US.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The DDoS protection is TCP only. While we do support UDP applications, if a UDP attack is received then UDP will be blocked until the DDoS attack stops.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All VPS services are unmanaged.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;More plans available here: https://billing.spartanhost.net/cart.php?gid=12&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Enter the coupon code &lt;b&gt;KVM20&lt;/b&gt; at the checkout for any VPS plan and get 20% recurring discount!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Terms of service: http://spartanhost.org/terms&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions or would like a custom quote, don't hesitate to email us at: &lt;a href="mailto:sales@spartanhost.net"&gt;sales@spartanhost.net&lt;/a&gt;, call us on &lt;b&gt;02895 813535&lt;/b&gt; if in the UK or &lt;b&gt;602 9105858&lt;/b&gt; if in the US or add us on Skype: &lt;b&gt;spartan_host&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
